"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    Será cancelada debido a nuestra incapacidad para renovarla.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
