#. module: tk_insurance_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tk_insurance_management.insurance_policy_approved_mail_template
msgid ""
"<table style=\"width: 100%\">\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <h4>\n"
"                                Dear Customer,\n"
"                                <br>\n"
"                                <strong>\n"
"                                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                                </strong>\n"
"                            </h4>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Your insurance claim has been approved after careful evaluation. It meets the eligibility criteria\n"
"                    outlined in your policy. We understand the importance of a timely resolution and are committed to\n"
"                    facilitating a smooth claims process. Here are the key details regarding your approved claim.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Claim Reference Number:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.claim_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Number:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_id.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Category:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Sub Category:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_sub_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Date of Approval:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.claim_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Claim Amount:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.amount_paid\"></span>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Please review the provided details for accuracy. Should you have any concerns, kindly contact our\n"
"                    customer support team at\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    or reply to this email. Our representatives are ready to assist you.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Next steps in the claims process will vary based on your specific claim. Our team will contact you\n"
"                    shortly to discuss further actions. Any additional requirements will be clearly communicated.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Congratulations on your approved insurance claim. We value your patience and cooperation. Our\n"
"                    priority is to support you and ensure a seamless settlement process.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for choosing\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . We value your trust and are committed to providing exceptional service and experiences.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Sincerely,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<table style=\"width: 100%\">\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            Estimada cliente,\n"
"                            <br>\n"
"                            <h4>\n"
"                                <strong>\n"
"                                    <t t-out=\"object.insured_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                                </strong>\n"
"                            </h4>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Esperamos que este correo electrónico lo encuentre bien. Nos complace informarle que su reclamo de póliza de seguro ha\n"
"                    sido aprobado. Después de una cuidadosa evaluación de la información proporcionada y las verificaciones necesarias,\n"
"                    han determinado que su reclamo cumple con los criterios de elegibilidad descritos en su póliza.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                  Entendemos la importancia de una resolución rápida y nos comprometemos a garantizar una solución sin problemas\n"
"                  proceso de reclamos. Por lo tanto, nos gustaría brindarle los siguientes detalles con respecto a su\n"
"                  Demanda aprobada.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Número de referencia del reclamo:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.claim_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Número de póliza:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_id.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                               Categoría de política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Subcategoría de póliza:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_sub_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Fecha de aprobación:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.claim_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Monto aprobado:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"format_amount(object.amount_paid, object.currency_id)\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Revise los detalles mencionados anteriormente y asegúrese de que sean precisos. Si tiene alguna inquietud o\n"
"                    discrepancias, póngase en contacto con nuestro equipo de atención al cliente en\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.agent_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    o respondiendo a este correo electrónico. Nuestros representantes estarán encantados de atenderle y solucionar cualquier\n"
"                    Preguntas que pueda tener.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                   Los siguientes pasos del proceso de reclamos dependerán de la naturaleza de su reclamo específico. Nuestro equipo\n"
